# Shadow Clone web/

# No environment variables are required.
#
# The web/ surface is a static-export Next.js site served locally by
# bin/shadow-clone.js (loopback bind, default port 4747). It reads no
# environment variables at runtime.
#
# This file is kept as a marker so first-time contributors see that the
# project intentionally has no env config — the pre-pivot Supabase/auth/
# NFT environment was removed in commit ad5341e.
